    {
      "id": "optimistic_8_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_8",
      "description": "Looking for an ultra-affordable ride to get you moving without a big investment? This budget-friendly vehicle is priced to fit tight budgets and serves as a practical option for drivers who need basic transportation! Be aware: this car is in poor condition, showing significant wear and may require some mechanical attention \u2014 so it's best suited for handy buyers or those with a trusted mechanic. At this price point, it's a great opportunity to get behind the wheel without breaking the bank!",
