    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good condition and offers a reliable, practical option for everyday driving. The exterior presents well overall, showing only minor surface scuffs and light wear consistent with normal use \u2014 no major dents or significant paint damage. The interior is clean and functional, with typical signs of regular use such as light wear on high-contact surfaces. Mechanically, the car runs well and has been maintained, making it a solid choice for a buyer seeking dependable transportation at a reasonable price.",
