      "description": "This car is in poor condition. The exterior has significant wear, including multiple dents, scratches, and noticeable paint deterioration. The interior shows heavy wear with damaged upholstery and worn surfaces. Mechanically, the car runs but has issues that will likely require attention. Suitable for buyers looking for a project vehicle or basic transportation on a tight budget.",
